1
00:00:49,709 --> 00:00:52,791
ln 689 A.D.

2
00:00:52,875 --> 00:00:58,249
upon Emperor Tang Gaozhong's death

3
00:00:58,250 --> 00:01:05,291
Empress Wu, a regent for 7 years,

4
00:01:07,875 --> 00:01:10,208
would soon be coronated

5
00:01:12,334 --> 00:01:16,916
as history's first female Emperor.

6
00:01:20,542 --> 00:01:23,791
Royal clansmen and founding officials

7
00:01:23,875 --> 00:01:27,833
resented a woman usurping the throne

8
00:01:30,625 --> 00:01:31,833
and colluded...

9
00:01:33,625 --> 00:01:35,666
to overthrow her reign.

10
00:01:38,667 --> 00:01:43,458
Behind its peaceful faÃ§ade the capital
was lurking with danger.

11
00:01:46,167 --> 00:01:49,916
All hell was about to break loose...

12
00:02:01,084 --> 00:02:05,874
Detective Dee and the Mystery
of the Phantom Flame

13
00:02:19,500 --> 00:02:23,291
The Empress hereby decrees:

14
00:02:23,375 --> 00:02:30,374
The Court of State Ceremonials shall
welcome Umayyad diplomat Aspar

15
00:02:30,459 --> 00:02:36,958
and escort him to the Towering Buddha
to revere the Empress's divine glory.

16
00:02:44,084 --> 00:02:46,999
This is Master Jia.

17
00:02:47,084 --> 00:02:49,916
The Buddha is sixty-six yards high

18
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:54,708
symbolizing the sixty-sixth heaven
or the ninth cloud.

19
00:02:54,792 --> 00:02:58,874
-Please translate for the General.
-I already explained it to the General.

20
00:02:58,959 --> 00:03:03,666
Does this project need
to be finished before the Coronation?

21
00:03:03,750 --> 00:03:06,791
The General asked
if it will be ready before the Coronation.

22
00:03:06,875 --> 00:03:11,958
Sure, or my life will not be spared.

23
00:03:21,417 --> 00:03:24,083
This is so spectacular!

24
00:03:24,167 --> 00:03:27,708
Huge resources have been spent on this.

25
00:03:27,792 --> 00:03:33,624
Two million catties of metal were used.
More than 1000 catties are melted each day.

26
00:03:33,709 --> 00:03:37,624
The temperature is too high here.

27
00:03:39,209 --> 00:03:41,666
Bring water and a towel for the General!

28
00:03:42,625 --> 00:03:47,166
It's too hot.
We need water to avoid dehydration.

29
00:03:53,459 --> 00:03:56,749
Who is the person in the painting?

30
00:03:56,834 --> 00:04:00,041
The General asked whose portrait this is.

31
00:04:00,125 --> 00:04:02,749
This is Lu Li, our Imperial Chaplain.

32
00:04:02,834 --> 00:04:06,291
He's very powerful
and trusted by the Empress!

33
00:04:06,375 --> 00:04:09,791
These are amulets
bestowed by the Chaplain.

34
00:04:09,875 --> 00:04:12,874
They can dispel evil and thwart disaster.

35
00:04:12,959 --> 00:04:15,124
Master Jia is here.

36
00:04:15,209 --> 00:04:19,333
Is somebody going to speak with him?
What shall we do?

37
00:04:19,417 --> 00:04:22,833
We had better speak up

38
00:04:22,917 --> 00:04:25,333
before lives are lost!

39
00:04:28,125 --> 00:04:30,083
Who should do that?

40
00:04:31,042 --> 00:04:33,249
You go.

41
00:04:35,459 --> 00:04:37,833
Let's go up from here.

42
00:04:37,917 --> 00:04:40,833
Today's so clear
we can see for miles from up there!

43
00:04:43,875 --> 00:04:45,499
Lift him up.

44
00:04:54,709 --> 00:04:58,416
This tubular pillar is crucial to the Buddha.

45
00:04:58,500 --> 00:05:03,291
It's 82 yards long
and made from one casting.

46
00:05:03,375 --> 00:05:05,916
It is surrounded by 81 steel chains.

47
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:08,708
In the face of hurricanes or earthquakes,
the chains will pull in the opposite direction,

48
00:05:08,792 --> 00:05:13,708
-preventing the Buddha from collapsing.
-They're here. Mind your step.

49
00:05:17,917 --> 00:05:21,708
General, these are the Buddha's two eyes.
And here...

50
00:05:21,792 --> 00:05:25,791
-Master Jia... Master Jia...
-What's the matter?

51
00:05:26,917 --> 00:05:30,416
Please go ahead.

52
00:05:30,500 --> 00:05:32,249
What is it?

53
00:05:32,334 --> 00:05:35,499
When you inspected the pillar yesterday,
you removed some amulets.

54
00:05:35,584 --> 00:05:39,499
-Should we put them back?
-They haven't been put back?

55
00:05:39,584 --> 00:05:43,041
Moving the amulets
will bring bad luck, so...

56
00:05:43,125 --> 00:05:47,041
ever since you moved them,
everybody has been scared.

57
00:05:49,459 --> 00:05:55,583
-Our work has been suffering.
-Put them back right away. Hurry up.

58
00:05:55,667 --> 00:05:58,249
This way, please.

59
00:06:06,917 --> 00:06:08,666
Please...

60
00:06:13,625 --> 00:06:19,499
Magnificent.
You can see the whole Empire from here.

61
00:06:19,584 --> 00:06:23,958
From here you'll be able to see
the Queen's Coronation.

62
00:06:24,042 --> 00:06:28,916
He says we can see
the Coronation stage from here.

63
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:33,458
From here it looks like the Sun
is very close to us. Marvellous.

64
00:06:33,542 --> 00:06:36,083
The General says...

65
00:06:44,250 --> 00:06:48,249
He's on fire! He's burning!

